Have you ever just wanna see the current community event stats instead of just looking at a singular bar slowly filling up? Then this tracker is for you!\n\nThis tracker tracks the event progress by getting the data straight from the Brawl News API and math it out (which actually provides accurate results somehow), and also contains several tried and tested (but not trusty) features like event completion estimation and average scoring speed! Also includes easter eggs.
